Nonetheless, in the coming sections, we will lay out
the landscape of approximate transformations. We have
seen that, in the bipartite setting, the hierarchy between
these transformations collapses as the optimal fidelity is
always achievable with a deterministic transformation.

approximate transformations. Then in Section IV B, we
